Class BinaryCheckData

java.lang.Object
  gov.nih.nlm.meme.integrity.BinaryCheckData
public class BinaryCheckData
extends Object

Used to track data values used by a BinaryDataIntegrityCheck. It roughly corresponds to table ic_pair.
